3,"uid":58983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最近在3月8日婦女節落過去天水圍，路程不是太遠。我在灣仔去，半個鐘頭都去到。我落去天水圍同很多基層組織和市民傾過他們面對的問題。他們提出領展帶來的問題，缺乏街市。帶我看過很多不同地方。政府可以設立街市，或在一些地方做墟市。我都看過，我覺得可行性高，如果我上任，我覺得可以推動。<br />\n曾俊華<br />\n<br />\n根據<span style=\"color: red;\">Google Map</span>預計，從灣仔開車或搭的士到天水圍，需時大約39分鐘，若乘搭公共交通工具，則需要1小時22分至1小時45分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n（曾梓洋攝） （曾梓洋攝）<br />\n有網民在曾俊華的Facebook留言，質疑半小時由灣仔到天水圍的說法。他的團隊也在Facebook回應，由灣仔告士打道88號出發，到港鐵天水圍站，按Google Map只要33分鐘。</blockquote><br />\n成日帶錯路"},{"pid":"46bc0ddfe225112c6c87b12fa24055b560c83b23","tid":162753,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"健吾都即刻抽水<br />\n勁低質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k988urv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk988urv.jpg&h=323130e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97cea7789e405a3e5d37c8ab0f390f5c12bc522e","tid":162753,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>健吾都即刻抽水<br />\n勁低質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k988urv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk988urv.jpg&h=323130e0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n總站去總站梗係耐啦<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc73d5dda9af29eacdb713931dfaedd64a5ff0eb","tid":162753,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>健吾都即刻抽水<br />\n勁低質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k988urv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk988urv.jpg&h=323130e0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家先知？佢一向都低質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n揸車好離地咩？香港咁多車主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da3fe6e76eae625aadb0f9c8b25ea8113ac348c","tid":162753,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>健吾都即刻抽水<br />\n勁低質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k988urv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk988urv.jpg&h=323130e0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然我唔鍾意曾俊華<br />\n單係968轉26字頭嘅車 唔塞車嘅話30分鐘真係正常<br />\n利申：住過幾年天水圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c7756a49085f5998345b88d6cd49d13e2d4f7d","tid":162753,"uid":90503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>灣仔去天水圍不嬲好快，西隧丁九大欖全部直通唔會塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申坐969x試過35～40分鐘到入境處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下佢咩時間去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n969x仲係繁時先有既路線都只係35～40分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繁時都咁既時間，我真係唔信其他時間入唔到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51276af0eb6563b583376713346bdad30291150d","tid":162753,"uid":414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>健吾都即刻抽水<br />\n勁低質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k988urv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk988urv.jpg&h=323130e0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家先知？佢一向都低質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n揸車好離地咩？香港咁多車主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條友柒左仲要死撐"},{"pid":"c0748a96b188